claim.claim-text:
1. An ankle assembly for a crash test dummy comprising:
an ankle clevis assembly for attachment to a leg assembly of the crash test dummy;
an ankle base assembly for attachment to a foot assembly of the crash test dummy and cooperating with said ankle clevis assembly;
a fastener to connect said clevis assembly and said ankle base assembly together to allow proper ankle positions for different ankles and also allow friction adjustment to simulate human bracing in impact conditions; and
a plurality of elastomeric elements disposed between said clevis assembly and said ankle base assembly that allow proper inversion and eversion performance of said ankle assembly.
